        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 23:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " states that the duty was discharged by 4,000 persons. Perhaps of the 93 chief porters here spoken of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 26:8-9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 26:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
